   - **Reader Page**: Focused heavily on readability, incorporating `Lora` typography for text and an AI integrated side-panel (showing summary, stats, and TOC navigation).

> [!NOTE]
> All these screens have been heavily focused around your "Rule of 3 Colors" (Warm darks, Amber, Violet) to keep the aesthetic highly premium and immersive.

## Next Steps

We have established the core experience! From here we can iteratively build out the rest of the 25+ views from the plan, or adjust the core style further. To view these newly generated UI pages, head over to your Stitch Projects dashboard.
